---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="测试页面" description="GitHub 推送测试" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🎉 链路测试成功！</h1>
			<p>如果你能看到这个页面，说明 GitHub 推送链路已经通了。</p>
			<p>当前时间：{new Date().toLocaleString('zh-CN')}</p>
			<hr />
			<a href="/">← 返回首页</a>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	h1 {
		color: #4CAF50;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
	}
	hr {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		border: none;
		border-top: 1px solid #eee;
	}
	a {
		color: #0066cc;
	}
</style>
